Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.24,0:00:05.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和重力波防護罩差不多嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.28,0:00:07.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個體護壁還真了得
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.37,0:00:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎 我們各自用不同的波長試試
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.25,0:00:12.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.95,0:00:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同化看來是辦不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.11,0:00:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來分析這傢伙的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.76,0:00:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我5秒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.87,0:00:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探明內核的位置了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.75,0:00:40.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好！
